SENATE AMENDMENT

SENATE AMENDMENT “ ” to COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “A” to H.P. 224, L.D. 324
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment changes the title and removes the substantive provisions of
33 Committee Amendment "A." It authorizes the Commissioner of Education to raise and
44 expend private funds to support a fund established for specific educational programs and
55 opportunities.
